article.description: — Alex Hunter had a career-high 24 points as Furman topped South Carolina Upstate 87-77 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hunter carries Furman past South Carolina Upstate 87-77
article.linkText: Hunter carries Furman past South Carolina Upstate 87-77
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — Alex Hunter had a career-high 24 points as Furman topped South Carolina Upstate 87-77 on Saturday. Hunter made 6 of 9 3-pointers. Jalen Slawson had 18 points for Furman (4-2). Marcus Foster added 15 points and 10 rebounds. Mike Bothwell had 11 points. Nick Alves had 16 points for the Spartans (2-4). Jordan Gainey added 13 points. Dalvin White had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
